<subSubSection pageId="14" pageNumber="119" type="distribution">
<paragraph pageId="14" pageNumber="119">Distribution.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="14" pageNumber="119">
<taxonomicName class="Mammalia" family="Cricetidae" genus="Microakodontomys" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Microakodontomys transitorius" order="Rodentia" pageId="14" pageNumber="119" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="transitorius">Microakodontomys transitorius</taxonomicName>
is endemic to the Cerrado, and has been recorded in the Brazilian Distrito Federal (
<bibRefCitation author="Hershkovitz, P" pageId="36" pageNumber="141" url="https://doi.org/10.5962/bhl.title.3370" year="1993">Hershkovitz 1993</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation pageId="14" pageNumber="119">Bonvicino et al. 2014</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation pageId="14" pageNumber="119">Paresque and Hanson 2015</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="14" pageNumber="119" type="conservation status">
<paragraph pageId="14" pageNumber="119">Conservation status.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="14" pageNumber="119">
The red list of the IUCN ver. 3.1 assigned the category 
<normalizedToken originalValue="“Endangered”">&quot;Endangered&quot;</normalizedToken>
to 
<taxonomicName class="Mammalia" family="Cricetidae" genus="Microakodontomys" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Microakodontomys transitorius" order="Rodentia" pageId="14" pageNumber="119" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="transitorius">Microakodontomys transitorius</taxonomicName>
(see 
<bibRefCitation author="Marinho-Filho, J" pageId="36" pageNumber="141" url="https://doi.org/10.2305/IUCN.UK.2010-2.RLTS.T136468A4295568.en" year="2010">Marinho-Filho and Vieira 2010</bibRefCitation>
). The species appears in the official list of threatened species of Brazil with the category 
<normalizedToken originalValue="“Endangered”">&quot;Endangered&quot;</normalizedToken>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Iack-Ximenes, GE" pageId="36" pageNumber="141" url="http://www.icmbio.gov.br/portal/images/stories/comunicacao/publicacoes/publicacoes-diversas/dcom_sumario_executivo_livro_vermelho_ed_2016.pdf" year="2016">ICMBIO-MMA 2016</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
